headline: NISSIN FOODS速 NAMED OFFICIAL PARTNER OF WWE速
summary: WWE, part of TKO Group Holdings (NYSE: TKO), and Nissin Foods today announced a new partnership that will see Hot & Spicy FIRE WOK, the company's hottest ramen brand, serve as a presenting partner of Elimination Chamber, which takes place Saturday, March 1 at Rogers Centre in Toronto.
